Detailed Use Cases:
Customer:
View Retailers

Browse a list of available retailers.

Select Products

Choose products from a retailer's catalog.

Place Order

Submit an order with selected products, quantity, and delivery details.

View Orders

Check past orders and their statuses.

Provide Feedback

Submit feedback for a retailer or specific product.

Retailer:
Register Retailer

Sign up as a retailer with name, phone, location, and TIN.

Login (TIN/Name)

Authenticate using TIN and name.

Manage Products

Add, edit, or delete products in their catalog.

View Orders

See incoming orders and update their status (Accept/Reject/Complete).

View Daily Sales

Check sales reports for the day (total sales, product-wise breakdown).

Edit Profile

Update retailer details (name, phone, location, TIN).

Relationships:
Both actors interact with the system independently.

Customers interact with retailers indirectly via orders and feedback.

Retailers manage their own products and orders.

